api_list.name: Logo and Icon
api_list.description: Get image generative with Logo and Icon Category
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://great-prompt.p.rapidapi.com/image/search/1/Logo%20Icon"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "great-prompt.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
